Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然改变了决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你可是100%信任啊 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我的绝对忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及识破纲手企图杀我的眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当 毕竟我也是医疗班出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才的查克拉充满了杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手 我可是真心想让他们两个复活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还答应了你不动木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那是你的花言巧语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想见他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想见见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想抱抱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想看看他们的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我即将看到绳树和断的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间 我突然发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉自己是一个多没用的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想到他们的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然就会全然不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢他们 真心爱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想再次拥抱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对…不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我看到那个小鬼后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了他们两人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我打算忘记的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子是爷爷的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保护它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是创立了这个村子的初代火影的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢这个村子 还有我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要像爷爷那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚会继承火影的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我要继承火影之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹死后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是靠这些回忆活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一定要成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为保护大家而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人不惜赌上生命想去实现的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想帮他们实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过“有形之物早晚会凋零”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个想法不会凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来交涉决裂了 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只能用力量逼你就范了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉决裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我至今好像还未和你交过手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可真敢说啊 她的对手是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你们全部就地解决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样 力量还是那么恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她打中一下就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里想拉开战斗距离有点拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算转移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和纲手大人的手下在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候会前来援助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的麻烦人物是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和您以及纲手大人同为三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来那位纲手公主下手不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 纲手大人拒绝他们的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手婆婆到底去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是纲手大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豚豚 在哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手的呼吸也变得急促了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体术并非我所长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵量丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个印是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼也会使用医疗忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉被…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我切断了您一部分的肱二头肌和腿部肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就使不出那种恐怖的怪力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉手术刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不直接攻击我的动脉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个手术刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可以在\N不留外伤的情况下切断血管和肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有足够的时间做出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以切断动脉\N心脏等地的查克拉手术刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过割断对手的喉咙还是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 胸肌被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不是普通的医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施术的才能和效果远超全盛期的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会割断你喉咙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样你应该动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就因为呼吸困难而动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有必要让她再吃些苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不杀死她的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明想动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚却动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前这状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使出这点力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她攻击的不是我的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是神经
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是神经
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把查克拉电子化 并将其电解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后注入你的神经系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑和身体能够进行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是通过电子信号沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手扰乱了时速360公里的运动电子信号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她久疏阵地战 居然还能保持这种实力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗术太消耗查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动右手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚就会动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动左脚脚踝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右肩就会动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么移动想动的部位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经基本掌握了八成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这种忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就能活动身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是怕看到血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让你看个够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见了 自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊 眼神那么凶恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你们认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起参加了中忍考试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么兜前辈会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙由我来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能活动身体也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵活度不可能像之前那么自如
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体终于恢复自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次面对两个三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少先干掉一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么兜前辈和纲手婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真迟钝啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你无法胜过佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看他的额头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是大蛇丸的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我是音忍派来的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 骗人的吧 兜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中忍考试时 你教给我很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了收集你们的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集了你的相关数据后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不具备作为一个忍者的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和佐助不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次看到纲手大人这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再一个人逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是您的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纲手婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再凶巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样可爱的下忍也不该来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对你体内寄生的怪物有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在传说中的三忍面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不过如同一只蝼蚁一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你敢多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只右手动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人一起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他无法防御的右边开始进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口针
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经反射系统还没完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲不开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中护额了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增血丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增血丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充失去的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子跟我一样 是医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血流得很是时候啊 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人 请拆下左手的绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大终于出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼镜的交给你处理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想再对纲手婆婆下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要按照赌约
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个不吉利的首饰送给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 愤怒的螺旋丸